# Talos EPP — first-party curated signature database (SHA-256).
#
# Format:  <sha256>  <Family/Label>
#
# This is Talos's own, growing hash-signature database. It is embedded into the
# binaries alongside baseline.hashdb and is grown from **vetted** feedback:
#   * locally, by the operator:  `talos scan <path> --json > scan.log`
#                                `talos ingest scan.log`
#   * upstream:  send a scan log; confirmed-malicious hashes are folded in here
#                and shipped to everyone in the next release.
#
# Only **confirmed-malicious** samples belong here — a hash signature is an
# exact-match fingerprint, so a false entry would flag that exact file forever.
# (Generalising detections — packers, families, behaviours — are better written
# as YARA rules under signatures/yara/.)
